---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

const lastUpdated = 'May 11, 2026'
const legalName = 'VP Promos LLC'
const dba = 'Bighorn Threads'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Bighorn Threads"
  description="Terms & Conditions for VP Promos LLC, doing business as Bighorn Threads — website use, quotes and orders, artwork, intellectual property, and SMS text-messaging program terms."
  canonical="https://bighornthreads.com/legal/terms/"
>
  <section class="border-b border-hairline bg-paper pt-14 pb-12 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="kicker">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-heading text-4xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal sm:text-5xl">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ash">
        {legalName} d/b/a {dba} &nbsp;·&nbsp; Las Vegas, Nevada &nbsp;·&nbsp; Last updated {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-concrete py-14 sm:py-20">
    <div class="legal mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p>
        These Terms &amp; Conditions (&ldquo;Terms&rdquo;) govern your use of
        <a href="https://bighornthreads.com">bighornthreads.com</a> (the &ldquo;Site&rdquo;) and the
        products and services offered by <strong>{legalName}</strong>, doing business as
        <strong>{dba}</strong> (&ldquo;Bighorn Threads,&rdquo; &ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;).
        By using the Site or submitting a request to us, you agree to these Terms and to our
        <a href="/legal/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>. If you do not agree, do not use the Site.
      </p>

      <h2>1. About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Bighorn Threads is a Las Vegas, Nevada custom-apparel and promotional-products shop providing
        screen printing, embroidery, branded workwear and safety apparel, company stores, and promotional
        products. &ldquo;Bighorn Threads&rdquo; is a registered fictitious-name (DBA) of {legalName}.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Use of the Site</h2>
      <p>
        You may use the Site only for lawful purposes. You agree not to misuse the Site, interfere with
        its operation or security, attempt unauthorized access, scrape or harvest data except as
        permitted, or use it to send spam or unlawful content. We may suspend or restrict access at our
        discretion.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Quotes, Orders &amp; Artwork</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Quotes are estimates.</strong> Prices quoted are based on the information you provide and current supplier pricing, and are not binding until we confirm a written order. Quantities, garment availability, decoration specs, and freight can change pricing.</li>
        <li><strong>Order confirmation.</strong> An order is accepted only when we confirm it in writing (email is sufficient). Production timelines begin after artwork approval and, where applicable, receipt of payment or deposit.</li>
        <li><strong>Artwork &amp; proofs.</strong> You are responsible for reviewing and approving digital proofs. We are not responsible for errors (spelling, layout, color, sizing, placement) approved by you. Screen, print, and thread colors may vary from on-screen previews.</li>
        <li><strong>Your content.</strong> By submitting logos, designs, text, or other materials, you represent that you own them or have all necessary rights, licenses, and permissions to use and reproduce them. You grant Bighorn Threads a non-exclusive, royalty-free license to copy, reproduce, modify (for fit/output reasons), display, and apply those materials to your ordered goods, and to use anonymized samples of finished work in our portfolio unless you tell us not to. You agree to indemnify us against claims arising from materials you supply.</li>
        <li><strong>Production variances.</strong> Industry-standard over/under runs, minor placement and color variances, and supplier substitutions of comparable items may occur.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        The Site and its content — text, graphics, logos, photographs, and layout — are owned by or
        licensed to Bighorn Threads and protected by intellectual-property laws. Product data and images
        are &copy; SAGE&reg; and the respective suppliers, used under license. You may not copy,
        reproduce, or republish Site content without our written permission. Brand names and trademarks
        referenced on the Site belong to their respective owners.
      </p>

      <h2>5. SMS / Text Messaging Program Terms</h2>
      <p>
        Bighorn Threads operates two separate text-messaging programs under our brand, each requiring its
        own explicit opt-in. You may opt in to either, both, or neither.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Bighorn Threads Customer Care (non-marketing).</strong> Texts related to your quote, order, and account — quote follow-ups, artwork-proof updates, production and delivery status, appointment reminders, and replies to questions you send us. Estimated frequency: typically 2–6 messages per active order; frequency otherwise varies based on your activity with us.</li>
        <li><strong>Bighorn Threads Promotions (marketing).</strong> Texts about special offers, discounts, new products, and seasonal promotions. Estimated frequency: up to 4 messages per month.</li>
        <li><strong>How you opt in.</strong> You opt in by checking the corresponding SMS consent box on a form at bighornthreads.com (for example, on our <a href="/contact/">contact / quote page</a> or an event sign-up page), or by giving us your number with written consent at an in-person event. Each program requires a separate, affirmative check; consent is never pre-selected.</li>
        <li><strong>Age requirement.</strong> You must be 18 years of age or older to use this SMS service.</li>
        <li><strong>Consent is not a condition of purchase.</strong> You are not required to opt in to text messages to request a quote, place an order, or otherwise do business with us.</li>
        <li><strong>Opt out (STOP) instructions.</strong> You may opt out of either SMS program at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong>, <strong>END</strong>, <strong>CANCEL</strong>, <strong>UNSUBSCRIBE</strong>, or <strong>QUIT</strong> to any message from that program. We will send one confirmation text and then stop sending you that program&rsquo;s messages. Opting out of one program does not opt you out of the other; opting out of marketing texts does not stop transactional texts about an active order, and vice versa. To rejoin, opt in again as you did initially. For assistance, reply <strong>HELP</strong> or <strong>INFO</strong>, or contact us at <a href="tel:+17029048923">(702) 904-8923</a> or <a href="mailto:info@bighornthreads.com">info@bighornthreads.com</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Carrier liability.</strong> Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</li>
        <li><strong>Rates &amp; frequency.</strong> As always, message and data rates may apply for messages sent to you from us and to us from you. For questions about your text plan or data plan, contact your wireless provider.</li>
        <li><strong>Privacy.</strong> Mobile information is used only to communicate with you about the program you opted in to. For more, see our <a href="/legal/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>. <strong>No mobile information will be shared with third parties or affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes. All the above categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.</strong></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Disclaimers</h2>
      <p>
        The Site and its content are provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; and &ldquo;as available&rdquo; without
        warranties of any kind, express or implied, including merchantability, fitness for a particular
        purpose, accuracy, or non-infringement. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted,
        error-free, or secure. Product availability and pricing are subject to change without notice.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, Bighorn Threads and {legalName} will not be liable for any
        indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or for lost profits or
        revenues, arising out of or related to your use of the Site or our services. Our total liability
        for any claim relating to an order will not exceed the amount you paid for that order.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Indemnification</h2>
      <p>
        You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Bighorn Threads, {legalName}, and their owners and
        employees from any claims, damages, liabilities, and expenses (including reasonable attorneys&rsquo;
        fees) arising out of your use of the Site, your breach of these Terms, or materials or
        instructions you provide to us.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Nevada, without regard to its conflict-of-laws
        rules. Any dispute will be brought exclusively in the state or federal courts located in Clark
        County, Nevada, and you consent to their jurisdiction.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these Terms from time to time. The &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date above reflects the
        most recent change. Your continued use of the Site after changes take effect means you accept the
        updated Terms.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>{legalName}</strong> d/b/a <strong>{dba}</strong><br />
        Las Vegas, Nevada, USA<br />
        Email: <a href="mailto:info@bighornthreads.com">info@bighornthreads.com</a><br />
        Phone: <a href="tel:+17029048923">(702) 904-8923</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    color: var(--color-ash);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .legal > p { margin-top: 1.15rem; }
  .legal > p:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .legal h2 {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }
  .legal ul {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.35rem;
    list-style: disc;
  }
  .legal ul li { margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .legal ul li::marker { color: var(--color-gold-500); }
  .legal strong { color: var(--color-charcoal); font-weight: 600; }
  .legal a {
    color: var(--color-gold-700);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .legal a:hover { color: var(--color-gold-600); }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .legal { font-size: 1.0625rem; }
    .legal h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
